parameters.text:
=You are a URL processing engine. Your only task is to update the "CURRENT_COMPANY" filter in a LinkedIn Sales Navigator URL.



**INSTRUCTIONS:**

1.  Analyze the [Base Link] provided below.

2.  Locate the section starting with `(type%3ACURRENT_COMPANY`.

3.  Replace the existing company list with the [New Company List] provided below.

4.  **Format each new company exactly as follows:**

    `(id%3Aurn%253Ali%253Aorganization%253A{ID}%2Ctext%3A{NAME}%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED%2Cparent%3A(id%3A0))`

    *(Note: Ensure the URL encoding matches the depth of the Base Link, typically %253A for colons).*

5.  Preserve all other filters (Region, Title, etc.) exactly as they are in the Base Link.

6.  Output ONLY the final valid URL. No text, no explanations.

**DATA INPUT:**

[Base Link]:
https://www.linkedin.com/sales/search/people?query=(recentSearchParam%3A(id%3A4072880329%2CdoLogHistory%3Atrue)%2Cfilters%3AList((type%3ACURRENT_COMPANY%2Cvalues%3AList((id%3Aurn%253Ali%253Aorganization%253A15564%2Ctext%3ATesla%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED%2Cparent%3A(id%3A0))))%2C(type%3ACURRENT_TITLE%2Cvalues%3AList((id%3A79%2Ctext%3AHuman%2520Resources%2520Specialist%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A45%2Ctext%3AHuman%2520Resources%2520Manager%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A91%2Ctext%3ARecruiter%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A444%2Ctext%3ARecruitment%2520Specialist%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A300%2Ctext%3AHuman%2520Resources%2520Assistant%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A105%2Ctext%3AHuman%2520Resources%2520Director%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A483%2Ctext%3AHuman%2520Resources%2520Executive%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A248%2Ctext%3AHuman%2520Resources%2520Consultant%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A271%2Ctext%3AHuman%2520Resources%2520Generalist%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A400%2Ctext%3AHuman%2520Resources%2520Coordinator%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A268%2Ctext%3ARecruitment%2520Consultant%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A495%2Ctext%3ATechnical%2520Recruiter%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A13195%2Ctext%3ASenior%2520Human%2520Resources%2520Recruiter%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A609%2Ctext%3ARecruitment%2520Manager%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A1094%2Ctext%3AInformation%2520Technology%2520Recruiter%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A921%2Ctext%3ADirector%2520of%2520Recruiting%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A1827%2Ctext%3ARecruitment%2520Coordinator%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A787%2Ctext%3AExecutive%2520Recruiter%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A2446%2Ctext%3ATalent%2520Acquisition%2520Specialist%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A4318%2Ctext%3ATalent%2520Management%2520Specialist%2CselectionType%3AINCLUDED)%2C(id%3A4288%2Ctext%3ATalent%2520Acquisition%2520Manager%2CselectionTyp
